'''Maurício Magalhães Prado''' (born 22 June 2001), simply known as '''Maurício''', is a professional [[footballer]] who plays as an [[attacking midfielder]] or [[right midfielder]] for [[Campeonato Brasileiro Série A|Série A]] club [[SE Palmeiras|Palmeiras]]. Born in Brazil, he plays for the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Career==
===Cruzeiro===
Maurício joined [[Cruzeiro Esporte Clube|Cruzeiro]] on loan from [[Desportivo Brasil]] ahead of the 2019 season. In November 2019, [[Cruzeiro Esporte Clube|Cruzeiro]] confirmed that they had signed Maurício for a fee around 800 thousand [[Brazilian real|R$]].<ref>[https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/cruzeiro/noticia/meia-atacante-mauricio-renova-com-cruzeiro-ate-2023-e-recebe-convocacao-da-selecao-sub-20.ghtml Meia-atacante Maurício renova com Cruzeiro até 2023 e recebe convocação da seleção sub-20], globoesporte.globo.com, 12 November 2019</ref>

===Internacional===
[[File:Mauricio at Internacional in 2023.png|thumb|left|150px|Maurício with [[Sport Club Internacional|Internacional]] in 2023]]
On 5 November 2020, Maurício was presented at [[Sport Club Internacional|Internacional]] in an exchange of players between ''Inter'' and Cruzeiro. He scored his first goal against [[Fluminense FC]].

On October 22, 2023, Maurício completed 150 games with the Inter shirt, in the historic victory over Santos, 7-1, in the Brazilian Championship.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ge.globo.com/rs/futebol/times/internacional/noticia/2023/10/23/em-tarde-de-garcom-mauricio-completa-150-jogos-pelo-inter-e-vibra-marca-importante.ghtml |title=Em tarde de garçom, Mauricio completa 150 jogos pelo Inter e vibra: "Marca importante" |language=pt |website=ge.globo.com |date=2023-10-23 |access-date=2024-06-24}}</ref>

===Palmeiras===
Maurício debuted on July 17, 2024, he played about 28 minutes in Rio de Janeiro. He dribbled, disarmed and showed his quality. In defeat, Palmeiras lost 1-0 to [[Botafogo de Futebol e Regatas|Botafogo]], at the Nilton Santos Stadium, in a game valid for the 17th round of the Brasileirão.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://portalcbncampinas.com.br/2024/07/felipe-anderson-deixa-boa-impressao-em-estreia-pelo-palmeiras/ | title=Felipe Anderson deixa boa impressão em estreia pelo Palmeiras | date=18 July 2024 }}</ref>

==International career==
Maurício was born in Brazil and is of Paraguayan descent through his paternal grandmother.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lanacion.com.py/futboledicion-impresa/2026/03/17/mauricio-un-sueno-por-la-abuela/|title=La Nación / Maurício, un "sueño" por la abuela|website=www.lanacion.com.py}}</ref> On August 2023, he was called up to the [[Brazil national under-23 football team|Brazil U23]]s for a set of friendlies.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onefootball.com/id/berita/mauricio-mediocampista-con-raices-paraguayas-convocado-a-la-seleccion-de-brasil-38066874|title=Maurício, mediocampista con raíces paraguayas, convocado a la selección de Brasil|date=10 February 2026|website=OneFootball}}</ref>

On 9 February 2026, Maurício's request to switch international allegiance to Paraguay was approved by [[FIFA]].<ref name="FIFA-CAP">{{cite news |url=https://knowledge.fifa.com/change-of-association-platform |title=FIFA Change of Association Platform |website=knowledge.fifa.com |date=10 February 2026|access-date=10 February 2026}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ge.globo.com/futebol/times/palmeiras/noticia/2026/02/11/mauricio-do-palmeiras-se-naturaliza-paraguaio-e-pode-jogar-a-copa-do-mundo.ghtml|title=Maurício, do Palmeiras, se naturaliza paraguaio e pode jogar a Copa do Mundo|trans-title=Maurício, from Palmeiras, becomes a naturalized Paraguayan citizen and could play in the World Cup|publisher=[[Grupo Globo|ge]]|language=pt-BR|date=11 February 2026|accessdate=11 February 2026}}</ref>

